### This document contains a list of common commands and their most useful flags.

ls

  ls -lah
    -l: long form
    -a: all files, including hidden files
    -h: human readable file sizes
  
  ls -lahtr
    -l: long form
    -a: all files, including hidden files
    -h: human readable file sizes
    -t: sort by time accessed
    -r: reverse order

  ls -lah --group-directories-first
    -l: long form
    -a: all files, including hidden files
    -h: human readable file sizes
    --group-directories-first: groups directories first in the listing


ps



cat
  cat -n
    -n: number all lines
     

du
  du -chs
    -c: produce a grand total 
    -h: human readable
    -s: summarize




